While this assignment is safe because `postAndWait` locks consistently on both threads, I'd prefer clarifying that by pattern as such:

``` java
final AtomicReference<...> rootNode = new AtomicReference<>(...);
postAndWait(() -> {
  rootNode.set(theThing);
});
```

